		      <p style="text-align:center;"><b> Time Critical Distributed Inventory Management</b></p>
		       <img class="img-responsive img-center hidden-xs hidden-mobile"
		       src="img/speaker1.png"  style="float:left; padding-right:20px;"></img>
		       
		       <img class="img-responsive img-center visible-xs visible-mobile"
		       src="img/speaker1.png" style="margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto"></img>		     		 
		      <b>Who?</b> Amit Sharma, CTO Zoomcar<br />		      		  
		      <b>When?</b> 4:00pm on 20th Nov 2015 (Friday)<br />		      
		      <b>Where?</b> Golden Jubilee Hall, ECE Department<br />
		      <b>What?</b> The talk is about: <br/ >
			1. Search - Show Me The Car<br/ >
			  2. Allocation - Give Me The Car<br/ >
			    3. Disaster Recovery - Who Moved My Car?<br/ >
			      <span class="more">
				More ...
			      </span>		      
			      <div style="display:none">
				<br />
				<b> About the Speaker</b><br />
				As the CTO of Zoomcar, Amit built the whole platform from scratch including the
				inventory system, the new
				website and native mobile
				apps for android and iphone
				within the first year. Right
				now he is involved with
				scaling the team and
				building processes to
				leverage technology for
				ensuring smooth operations
				and consistent user
				experience. Prior to joining
				Zoomcar, Amit co-founded
				Khojguru.com, one of the
				leading discount coupon
				service on the internet in
				India. At Khojguru.com, Amit
				built the whole platform
				grounds-up and scaled it to
				3 million average monthly
				visitors and 1 million
				registered users, while
				restricting to a limited
				budget. Amit is a graduate in Electrical Engineering from IIT Delhi.   
 
				 <br/><br />

				<b> About the Company</b><br />
				Zoomcar is a Self-Drive car
				rental service which allows
				you to rent cars by the
				hour, day, week, or
				month. We have a wide
				variety of cars available
				across many
				locations. Basically, we
				save you the cost and hassle
				of owning a car while giving
				you all the good things
				about owning a car:
				convenience, mobility, and
				independence. Zoomcar
				officially hit the roads of
				India in February 2013 with
				just 7 cars available at a
				single location in
				Bangalore. At present, we
				have a fleet of about 2000
				vehicles across more than
				250 locations in Bangalore,
				Chennai, Delhi, Hyderabad,
				Mumbai and Pune. We offer
				more than 10 models covering
				hatch-backs, sedans, SUVs and 
				luxury cars. <br/><br /> 
 
				
